PR Title: FEAPP-420: Allow customer notification via WhatsApp
PR Description:
WHAT:
Update made to product listing should be notified via WhatsApp as well, along with Email.
NOTES:
Allow customer to enter WhatsApp number to get notification and also an option for selecting notification medium.
WHY:
WhatsApp is easy and more frequently used as compared to email.
PR Reviewers:
John Cena, Mary Kom
